content: That sounds like a great recipe. I've already tried making homemade granola once, and it turned out amazing. I've been snacking on it all week. Speaking of snacks, I've been trying to cut down on junk food, but I did give in to a sale on potato chips last week and ended up eating an entire bag in one sitting while watching TV - not my finest moment. Do you have any tips on how to resist junk food cravings?
